# set -e 收紧整条 hook（tech-debt #30）：2026-05-29 之前四条命令未串联，husky 只认
# 最后一条（unit test）的退出码，导致失败的 lint-staged / tsc / docs-drift 被静默放行。
# 加 set -e 后任一非零即中止提交。注意：lint-staged 只 lint 暂存文件，故未触碰文件里的
# 存量 error（9 个 react-hooks 组件 on-touch 债）不会挡住提交。
# 详见 docs/exec-plans/active/post-refactor-cleanup.md Phase D。
set -e

node scripts/lint-hooks.mjs
npx lint-staged
npx tsc --noEmit
# CODEX_DISABLED=1 mirrors `npm run test:unit` (see package.json scripts).
# Without it the pre-commit hook spawns the real Codex app-server during
# unit tests, which (a) holds the user's real CodePilot SQLite DB and
# fights for locks with the dev server, (b) takes ~35× longer than the
# standalone npm run test (~25s) — observed in Phase 5b round-6 smoke,
# where every commit wedged for 30+ minutes. Keep the hook env aligned
# with the canonical test script.
CODEX_DISABLED=1 npx tsx --test src/__tests__/unit/*.test.ts
